ghter, refreshed, healthy-looking complexion and can be added to your personalized facial plan.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day10_led_therapy.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 7, "date": "Wed, Jul 29", "scheduledAt": "2026-07-29T15:00:00Z", "title": "Microneedling: Skin Regeneration", "hook": "Help your skin renew from within.", "copy": "Microneedling supports your skin’s natural renewal process for a smoother, brighter, more refreshed-looking complexion.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day12_microneedling_regeneration.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 8, "date": "Thu, Jul 30", "scheduledAt": "2026-07-30T15:00:00Z", "title": "BOTOX® Cosmetic: Forehead Lines", "hook": "Refreshed, never overdone.", "copy": "A personalized BOTOX® Cosmetic consultation can help you explore a natural-looking approach to smoothing the appearance of forehead lines.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day05_servicio_spotlight.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 9, "date": "Fri, Jul 31", "scheduledAt": "2026-07-31T15:00:00Z", "title": "Microneedling: Texture Renewal", "hook": "Smoother-looking skin starts with a plan.", "copy": "A customized microneedling plan can support a more refined-looking texture and a fresh, healthy-looking glow over time.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day20_microneedling_texture.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 10, "date": "Sat, Aug 1", "scheduledAt": "2026-08-01T15:00:00Z", "title": "Botox Party 🎉", "hook": "Bring your crew. Celebrate your glow.", "copy": "Gather a group of three or more fo