ation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day10_led_therapy.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 23, "date": "Fri, Aug 14", "scheduledAt": "2026-08-14T15:00:00Z", "title": "BOTOX® Cosmetic: Neck Bands", "hook": "Explore a natural-looking refresh.", "copy": "A personalized BOTOX® Cosmetic consultation can help you learn whether treatment for the appearance of neck bands is right for your goals.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day06_botox_cosmetic.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 24, "date": "Sat, Aug 15", "scheduledAt": "2026-08-15T15:00:00Z", "title": "Microneedling: Pigmentation Concerns", "hook": "Help your complexion look more even and renewed.", "copy": "A personalized microneedling plan may support the appearance of a more even-looking skin tone and smoother texture.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day26_microneedling_pigmentation.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 25, "date": "Sun, Aug 16", "scheduledAt": "2026-08-16T15:00:00Z", "title": "Personalized Facial + Skin Consultation", "hook": "The best facial plan starts with listening.", "copy": "We’ll analyze your skin, deliver a personalized facial treatment, and map out a simple plan for your goals.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary consultation!", "footer": "📍 Cielo Vista Mall, El Paso TX | 📞 (915) 209-2060", "img": "day02_facial_consultation.jpg", "type": "Service", "client": true}, {"day": 26, "date": "Mon, Aug 17", "scheduledAt": "2026-08-17T15:00:00Z", "title": "PRP Hair Restoration", "hook": "Thinning hair? Start with a conversation.", "copy": "PRP Hair Restoration is available for women and men seeking support for healthier-looking hair and confidence.", "cta": "📲 Message us 'GLOW' for a complimentary